                    <div class="text-center">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-yellow-500 uppercase mb-4"><i class="fas fa-eye mr-2"></i> Visi</h3>
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
                            <p class="text-gray-800 font-bold italic text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">"Menciptakan siswa berakhlak, berprestasi dan siap kerja"</p>
